OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782908305
OL,3,CFly-tipper fined for 'stupid decision'
OL,4,Cto dump friend's sofa
OL,6,FCCTV footage captures a driver
OL,7,Ftransporting the sofa on his car roof
OL,8,Fbefore dumping it
OL,10,FA driver has been fined #1,722 after
OL,11,Fbeing caught on camera dumping a sofa
OL,12,Fin a residential area.
OL,14,FJayden Williams from Wolverhampton
OL,15,Fadmitted he made a "stupid decision"
OL,16,Fto leave the furniture in Racecourse
OL,17,FRoad at around 10pm on 22 August 2025.
OL,19,FHe told Dudley Magistrates Court he
OL,20,Fwas helping a friend who was having a
OL,21,Fclear out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
