PN,34702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782908305
OL,3,CFly-tipper fined for 'stupid decision'
OL,4,Cto dump friend's sofa
OL,6,FCity of Wolverhampton Council said the
OL,7,Ffine will be reinvested to tackle
OL,8,Fenvironmental crime, like fly-tipping.
OL,10,FHe was linked to the dumped furniture
OL,11,Fafter a local business supplied CCTV
OL,12,Ffootage to the council showing a sofa
OL,13,Fstrapped to the top of a BMW, which
OL,14,Fwas registered to Williams.
OL,16,FHe was served with a fixed penalty
OL,17,Fnotice (FPN) of #1,000. Williams
OL,18,Facknowledged the fine and requested an
OL,19,Fextension to pay it, which was granted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,348,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782908305
OL,3,CFly-tipper fined for 'stupid decision'
OL,4,Cto dump friend's sofa
OL,6,FHowever, he missed the extension
OL,7,Fdeadline and ignored the council's
OL,8,Fattempts to contact him.
OL,10,FWilliams was fined #730 and ordered to
OL,11,Fpay a victim surcharge of #292, and
OL,12,Fcosts of #700.
OL,14,FCouncillor Qaiser Azeem said: "Fly-
OL,15,Ftipping has a real impact on our city
OL,16,Fand on our residents ` it causes
OL,17,Fenvironmental harm and can affect
OL,18,Fcommunity pride.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
