CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F347A1782908305
OL,3,CFly-tipper fined for 'stupid decision'
OL,4,Cto dump friend's sofa
OL,6,F"This successful prosecution sends a
OL,7,Fclear message that the thoughtless
OL,8,Fdumping of waste will not be tolerated
OL,9,Fin Wolverhampton.
OL,11,FHe added: "We are investing in
OL,12,Fenforcement and anyone caught fly
OL,13,Ftipping can expect to face the
OL,14,Fconsequences."
